[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Created : reject
Approved : entry / log housekeeping
Created --> Draft : confirm
Draft --> Processing : update
Processing --> Completed : cancel
Processing : entry / log housekeeping
Completed --> Reviewed : update
Created --> Processing : revert
Reviewed --> [*]
